[White "1) 2.e4 The Blackmar Diemer Gambit"]
[Black "4.f3 Bf5 5.fxe4 Nxe4 #1"]
[Result "*"]

1. d4 d5 2. e4
{ This is called the Blackmar-Diemer Gambit @@StartBracket@@BDG@@EndBracket@@. White is trying to unbalance the center by offering a pawn. However, this sacrifice is inappropriate, and if Black knows how to deal with this gambit, then it's relatively easy to get an advantage. You are most likely to encounter  2.e4  in online games. }
2... dxe4 { Black accepts the sacrifice. } 3. Nc3 Nf6 4. f3
