{ This move was picked up by Rapport and Jobova a few years back and it has been quite popular since then. White's main idea oftentimes is to quickly develop the queenside pieces and go for the long castle. }
3... c5 4. e4
{ A tricky move. I believe that it is worth paying some attention to it. White immediately unbalances the center. }
4... Nxe4 { Accepting the sacrifice. } 5. Nxe4 dxe4 6. dxc5 Qa5+
