10. Qc4 { White wishes to exchange queens, but Black can simply refuse it. }
10... Qf5
{ I believe Black is slightly better thanks to their healthy position. Next is ...Bg7, ...O-O & Be6. If White intuitively plays  11.Bd3  , attacking the black queen, it is advisable to counterattack with  11...Be6  and after the queen exchange, the position is equal. }
