{ The key point of @@StartFEN@@rnbqk2r/pp3ppp/3bpn2/2pp4/3P1B2/2P1PN2/PP3PPP/RN1QKB1R w KQkq - 1 6@@EndFEN@@  6.Bb5+  . White is now threatening to go Qa3 pinning the pawn and will try to develop with Nbd2-Nb3. Black has to solve this issue. }
