{ A creative way to use the e5-pawn. Black has to play a few good moves to secure equality. }
21... h5
{ Black is creating counterplay by pushing the h-pawn. It also opens the Black back rank. White does not really have direct threats, as taking the c6-pawn would make White position difficult. }
