11. Nd2
{ 11.Nc3  This would leave no space for the queen to retreat to c2 after  11...Nxe5  12.Qb3  Bg7=  Black has the initiative. }
11... Be6 12. Qc2 O-O-O
{ The position is unbalanced but roughly equal. I believe that Black has the initiative, and White has to show some defensive moves in order to get a playable position as seen in the game Rapport - Dominguez which ended in a draw. }
