14... Bxb3
{ A very important rule, that I myself employ as well, is to always look for tactics. Here it not only saves the game but gives a better position. Note that before playing @@StartFEN@@r3kbnr/p2n1ppp/b1p5/q3P3/Ppp1P3/5N2/1PQB1PPP/RN2KB1R b KQkq - 4 10@@EndFEN@@  10...Nxe5  , Black has to already see that @@StartFEN@@r3kbnr/p4ppp/2p5/2q5/Ppb1P3/1P2B3/2Q2PPP/RN2K2R b KQkq - 1 14@@EndFEN@@  14...Bxb3  works, otherwise problems could occur. }
