Rxc1 15. Qxc1 e5 { Chasing the knight away so the black bishop can go to b5. }
16. N4f3 Bb5
{ Black is much better, because of White's misplaced pieces. Rd1 would run into ...Be2 losing an exchange. Nc4 would lose a piece to ...Qc7. }
