{ We have reached an endgame where White is seemingly slightly better, but I believe with a couple of accurate moves, the position is equal. }
21... Rc8 22. f4 { A logical move to make Rc1 possible. } 22... Be7 23. Rac1
{ White wants to take control over the c-file, but it does not promise more than equality. }
23... Rxc1 24. Rxc1 f6 { Chasing the bishop away. } 25. Rc8+ Kf7 26. Rxg8 Kxg8
27. Bd4 Kf7 { This bishop endgame is equal. Next is ...Bd6, ...f5. } *

