{ This natural-looking move is not good for White, as it lets Black finish their development in peace. }
12... Qb8
{ The bishops and the queen are very powerful. This move also steps out of the d-file tactics like Nxe6. }
13. h3 O-O
{ Black is better not only because of their well-placed pieces, but also because of the misplaced white bishop on b3. Next is ...Rc8, Nf8-Ng6. }
