{ Black chooses the typical setup. Black's plan is quite simple with ...Bd6, ...O-O. }
10. Nc3
{ This is the mainline of the 7. Qe2 line. White prepares the move e4 as in most lines. Note that the idea behind delaying the move e4 for White is that if Black takes  10...cxd4  now, then White could take back with  11.exd4!  and get an advantage. }
