1. d4 d5 2. c4 c6
{ This is the Slav Defense, however, a few moves later we will transpose to the QGA. }
3. Nc3 dxc4 4. e4 b5 5. a4
{ We transposed to @@StartFEN@@rnbqkbnr/pppppppp/8/8/8/8/PPPPPPPP/RNBQKBNR w KQkq - 0 1@@EndFEN@@  1.d4  d5  2.c4  dxc4  3.e4  b5  4.a4  c6  5.Nc3  . You will find my explanation of this line with much more details here. }
5... b4 6. Nb1
{ This is one of the main moves. The other two options are  6.Na2  as in Shirov - Vitiugov, the other is  6.Nce2  . }
6... Ba6 7. Qc2 Nf6
{ 7...e5!  I recommend the immediate breakthrough in my course. I think it promises a better game for Black. }
